properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued February 15 at 4:06AM AKST until February 16 at 6:00AM AKST by NWS Juneau AK
properties.description:
* WHAT...Snow. Total accumulations of 3 to 6 inches.

* WHERE...Elfin Cove, Pelican, and Juneau.

* WHEN...From noon today to 6 AM AKST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Plan on slippery road conditions.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Light snow will continue through this
morning. Heavier snowfall will being this afternoon into
tonight. Snowfall amounts will be highly variable due to the
showery nature of the precipitation.
properties.instruction:
Slow down and use caution while traveling.

An advisory means that a potentially hazardous event is already
occurring or imminent.

NWSheadline: WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM NOON TODAY TO 6 AM AKST SUNDAY
